OL,3,CNI Commonwealth Games office closed
OL,4,Camid threats over flag change proposal
OL,6,FThe office of Commonwealth Games
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland (CWGNI) has been
OL,8,Fclosed amid online threats over a
OL,9,Fproposal to change the flag that
OL,10,Frepresents the region's athletes.
OL,12,FCWGNI chief executive Conal Heatley
OL,13,Fsaid the office in Belfast would be
OL,14,Fclosed for a few days while a security
OL,15,Fassessment is conducted.
OL,17,FHe said the move came after
OL,18,Fthreatening messages were directed at
OL,19,Fthe office online and some of his
OL,20,Fpersonal details appeared on social
OL,21,Fmedia.
