OL,3,CNI Commonwealth Games office closed
OL,4,Camid threats over flag change proposal
OL,6,FThe threats emerged following
OL,7,Fpublicity over a proposal to replace
OL,8,Fthe Ulster Banner flag currently used
OL,9,Fto represent Northern Ireland athletes
OL,10,Ftaking part in the Commonwealth Games.
OL,12,FMr Heatley said the proposal reflected
OL,13,Fconcerns that the flag, which does not
OL,14,Fhave any official status in Northern
OL,15,FIreland, is not representative of or
OL,16,Fembraced by the whole community in the
OL,17,Fregion.
