OL,6,FIn an interview with the News Letter,
OL,7,FMr Heatley also said the flag had been
OL,8,Fused in recent targeting of homes of
OL,9,Fmembers of ethnic minority communities
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland, insisting that
OL,11,Fwas "not something we want to be
OL,12,Fassociated with".
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, DUP minister Gordon Lyons
OL,15,Fsaid the proposal to change the flag
OL,16,Fwas "ill-advised" and should be
OL,17,Fscrapped.
