OL,6,FSocial Development Minister Mr Lyons,
OL,7,Fwho has responsibility for sporting
OL,8,Fissues, said he had not been consulted
OL,9,Fabout the issue.
OL,11,F"I have to say, I believe that the
OL,12,Fcampaign we are currently hearing
OL,13,Fabout is ill-advised at best," he told
OL,14,Fthe Assembly.
