OL,6,F"I was concerned to learn about the
OL,7,Fdiscussion and consideration of
OL,8,Fchanging the flag. As we have seen at
OL,9,Fthe Olympics, our athletes have always
OL,10,Fkept their focus on sport and were
OL,11,Fable to represent Northern Ireland,
OL,12,Fand politics wasn't made anything of.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, I think politics has
OL,15,Fbeen dragged into this now. This was
OL,16,Fsomething I've not been consulted on.
