OL,6,F"If I had been consulted, I would have
OL,7,Fmade it very clear that I do not think
OL,8,Fthat we should be upsetting the status
OL,9,Fquo on this, that we have had athletes
OL,10,Fthat have been very happy to represent
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland at the Commonwealth
OL,12,FGames.
OL,14,F"They should continue to be allowed to
OL,15,Fdo so. I think that it's best for
OL,16,Feveryone involved if this was just to
OL,17,Fbe put to bed."
